data.description: This home has something for everyone! Wide open, extra large kitchen and dining area and TONS of space to entertain! HUGE wrap around deck, complete with a remote controlled Sunsetter retractable awning, overlooking an absolutely gorgeous nearly 13 acres. Tastefully rustic, this impressive home has 6 bdrms including a master suite that truly lives up to its name! In this suite you'll find your very own wood-burning stove and more than enough room for a full living room sectional, plus your full bedroom set! You won't be lacking for space in this 5,201 square foot home! Oh, and don't worry about the heating bills, there's a Nature's Comfort Outdoor Wood Furnace that will heat your entire home and water during the winter! This fantastic place truly has it all!!! There is simply too much to mention so call your agent today!
